Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:48.96,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Are you serious！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.92,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}No No No don't worry  One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:53.13,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}沉默的心臟 再次傳來跳動的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.38,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}即使視野很混亂 但是不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:05.52,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}你還相信著 我不會背叛你
