Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:11.31,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}即使孤單著 就算時光變遷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.69,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}還是學會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.99,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}嶄新的一天還會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.41,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}這個願望 即使沒有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.49,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}我也誓要實現它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:26.95,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}我們彼此還有眾多憧憬的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.37,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}所以即使想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:33.34,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}還是心有不甘 也不能止步不前
